																		Post of The Author
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250136" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;" >LordStonefish</a></span> <span class="odate time_1526855645 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">20 May 2018 22:34</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3806903">
									

<p>Part Three of the Doomsday Contest team with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1526855644" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;">WrongJohnSilver</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1526855644" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;">Cyantreuse</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1526855644" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span>. Special thanks to the critique from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1526855644" alt="Dr Aers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;">Dr Aers</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1526855644" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span>.</p>
<p>The image is from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borzoi#/media/File:Chart_rosyjski_borzoj_rybnik-kamien_pl.jpg">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borzoi#/media/File:Chart_rosyjski_borzoj_rybnik-kamien_pl.jpg</a></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Is&nbsp;this&nbsp;a&nbsp;GoI&nbsp;format?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;&nbsp;Is&nbsp;this&nbsp;a&nbsp;GoI&nbsp;format?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>No. This GoI only exists within the canon of our Contest story. It cannot function within the normal Foundation canon nor should it appear there. This is using the nature of the GoI format to tell a larger story.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;What's&nbsp;going&nbsp;on&nbsp;here?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;&nbsp;What's&nbsp;going&nbsp;on&nbsp;here?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>The Masquerade has been forgotten. The Foundation still functions at containing, but the oncoming wave of Lethe Events have deleted the concept of the Veil from the boundaries of the UN. The world looks a lot different now, and groups like the Astrolabe Institute can flourish in this faux Broken Masquerade.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

