<p>I honestly had no idea what I was reading at any point before looking at the comments, and the rehash of &quot;forgetting what dogs are&quot; thing wasn't terribly interesting.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Dr. F. Johansson: We are a Scientific Journal of the Anomalous, remember?</p>
<p>Mr. Byron: Did you?</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Also, this exchange makes no sense.</p>

